{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a Shopify Online Store 2.0 custom section called “Guide Spotlight – Signature Bio”.
    
    Layout:
    - Full-width section with warm ivory background and generous padding (desktop 100px top/bottom, mobile 70px).
    - Center container max-width 1180px.
    - Two-column layout on desktop:
      - Left: tall portrait image (about 46–50% width)
      - Right: text content (about 50–54% width), vertically centered
    - Mobile: image on top, text below, left-aligned on mobile with comfortable spacing.
    
    Design details (make it feel UNIQUE and editorial):
    - Image is displayed like a “framed print”:
      - Add an offset frame behind the image (a slightly darker ivory rectangle) shifted down/right by 14px.
      - Add a thin border around the image and a soft shadow.
      - Optional: add a tiny “tape” corner detail (small rotated rectangle) on the top edge for a collage feel (subtle, premium).
    - On the text side:
      - Eyebrow (editable): uppercase, wide tracking, gold accent.
      - Name: large serif (dark charcoal).
      - Add a “handwritten underline” stroke beneath the name using an SVG path (gold accent).
      - Role line: smaller, gold or muted tone.
      - Bio: paragraph text, muted gray, line height ~1.7.
      - Add optional mini-stat blocks under the bio (2–3 items) like “10+ years”, “Hundreds guided”, “Somatic healing” (as repeatable blocks).
    
    Settings/schema:
    - Image picker (primary portrait)
    - Optional second image (hover swap)
    - Eyebrow text, Name text, Role text, Bio rich text
    - Stats blocks (label + value)
    - Accent color, background color, text color
    - Toggle: show/hide stats
    - Toggle: enable animations
    
    Animations (animate EVERYTHING; run once when in view):
    - Background: subtle fade-in + a soft gradient “wash” that moves very slightly from left to right (2s).
    - Image: “polaroid settle” entrance:
      - Starts slightly rotated (-1.5deg) and scaled (1.03), then settles to 0deg and 1.0 with ease-out.
      - Reveal the image using a mask wipe from bottom to top (clip-path).
    - Offset frame behind image slides in from the left (small distance).
    - Eyebrow: stamp-in (opacity + tiny scale pop) and tracking tightens slightly.
    - Name: masked reveal + underline draws itself (SVG stroke-dash animation).
    - Role + bio: staggered fade-up (role first, then bio).
    - Stats: each stat fades up, and the number does a quick count-up (only if it’s numeric).
    - Hover micro-interactions (desktop):
      - Image gently zooms to 1.04.
      - If second image is provided, crossfade to it on hover (slow, premium).
      - Underline gets a tiny shimmer sweep (once).
    - Respect prefers-reduced-motion: no rotation, no count-up, no wipes—just simple fade-in.
    
    Technical requirements:
    - No external libraries.
    - Use IntersectionObserver to add “is-visible” classes.
    - All animation values controlled via CSS variables for easy tuning.
    
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
